This directory (test_Ar_Ne_periodic_B2_NEIGH_RVEC_f90) contains a test that
computes the minimum energy/cell of an infinite perfect B2 (CsCl-type) crystal of
Argon and Neon as a function of lattice spacing.

Makefile                                   -- makefile to compile and build executables with 
                                              GNU or Intel compilers
README                                     -- this file
test_Ar_Ne_periodic_B2_NEIGH_RVEC_f90.F90  -- Code for the test
test_Ar_Ne_periodic_B2_NEIGH_RVEC_f90.kim  -- KIM descriptor file for the test
